## Artifacts

Never commit large data, checkpoints, or workbench outputs. They are gitignored (`artifacts/`, `checkpoints/`, `packages/dataset/data/raw/`, `hf_release/`, `workbench/`). Regenerate via CLI or track with DVC when stages exist.
